{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": false, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 113107, "create_time": 1652423684, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "dz觉得自己很低能，可能甚至正确完整的价值观还没有建立起来", "timestamp": 1652423684}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 113109, "create_time": 1652423754, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "比如对很多事件，dz做出的判断往往只是基于自己个人的经验和情感", "timestamp": 1652423754}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 113113, "create_time": 1652423855, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "有没有可能，世界上就应当存在一些dz这样什么都不懂的傻逼来做韭菜呢", "timestamp": 1652423855}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 113115, "create_time": 1652423896, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "历史系本人 先看看《人类简史》", "timestamp": 1652423896}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 113121, "create_time": 1652423972, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 谢谢Alice！dz去看看", "timestamp": 1652423972}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 113305, "create_time": 1652432045, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "能意识到这一点已经很厉害了", "timestamp": 1652432045}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 113419, "create_time": 1652439620, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "毛选吧", "timestamp": 1652439620}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 114512, "create_time": 1652504134, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "斯塔夫里阿诺斯《全球通史》\n快速知道全球历史大概是个什么演化过程", "timestamp": 1652504134}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 114528, "create_time": 1652504794, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "楼上两本书对我的价值观塑造起了很大作用，很值得看；再推荐永远的经典《资本论》，以及米尔斯《社会学的想象力》", "timestamp": 1652504794}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 114530, "create_time": 1652504880, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "个人观点：也可以关注一些人文社科的科普类公众号，碎片化时间看看，节奏型的那种就少看或者理性看了（这里不做具体推荐）", "timestamp": 1652504880}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 114544, "create_time": 1652505554, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Eve: 资本论一般人是读不下去的。恩格斯写过若干小册子，想初步了解共产主义理论可以看看。或者直接买本考研政治（", "timestamp": 1652505554}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 114583, "create_time": 1652507884, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "雾都孤儿双城记拜伦雪莱萧伯纳", "timestamp": 1652507884}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 115508, "create_time": 1652537859, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "我还以为是我自己", "timestamp": 1652537859}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 116729, "create_time": 1652604607, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 8, "text": "资本论对于学经济学和政治学来说时是很糟糕的书，资本论是用来学习政治（政治学和政治完全不同）的。《人类简史》挺不错，提供了一种新的认识事物运行发展的思路；起类似作用的书还有《钢铁、枪炮和细菌》和《自私的基因》等。缺点是只看某本书可能会剑走偏锋，以偏概全。经济学（尤其指基于供给均衡构造的微观经济学，例如芝加哥学派）的书推荐《一课经济学》或者薛兆丰的《经济学通识》（后面这本书更好看）。方法论和自我认识的书，推荐李笑来的《把时间当做朋友》。视频音频节目推荐《罗辑思维》，以及《睡前消息》。罗辑思维的逻辑侵略性比较强，注意保持批判性；睡前消息偏向实事分析，目前还在每周三期更新。", "timestamp": 1652604607}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 116790, "create_time": 1652606525, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Hans: 《睡前消息》存疑（\n批判着看\n历史可以看看小约翰可汗，当然也要批判着看", "timestamp": 1652606525}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 117405, "create_time": 1652622978, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 8, "text": "Re Dave: 睡前消息是很严肃的节目，但是不够严谨，不过错误的地方基本都修正了；以及观点鲜明，可能会造成一些洗脑效果。可汗还是偏向娱乐，分析和论述比较少。", "timestamp": 1652622978}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 117660, "create_time": 1652629027, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 9, "text": "Re Hans: 小约翰可汗的节目基本是图一乐，而且了解一些狠人的故事对你真的了解历史帮助不大，不过如果你看完一个奇葩小国之后有工夫沉下心来仔细了解这个国家的历史还是非常不错的", "timestamp": 1652629027}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 117906, "create_time": 1652635473, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Isabella: 是这样的，奇葩小国系列质量很高了，主要是dz不是就想有个大概了解么，小约翰可汗绰绰有余了", "timestamp": 1652635473}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 121303, "create_time": 1652782410, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 10, "text": "不如去看看天涯社区kkndme的帖子，比较有意思", "timestamp": 1652782410}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 130061, "create_time": 1653112526, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 11, "text": "#政治\n#历史", "timestamp": 1653112526}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 131405, "create_time": 1653146489, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 12, "text": "Re : 玩钢铁雄心4", "timestamp": 1653146489}], "create_time": 1652423635, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1653146489, "likenum": 62, "n_attentions": 62, "n_comments": 21, "pid": 40385, "poll": null, "reply": 21, "text": "完全不懂政治和历史，应该怎样提高自己的知识水平呢？比如有哪些书可以读", "timestamp": 1652423635}}